c: 7
v: 156
t: "wajaealna mmn ktbt lah alsaalihat min al'aemal fi aldunya wafi alakhirati, 'iinaa rajaena tayibin 'iilayka, qal allah taealaa limusaa: eadhabi 'usib bih man 'asha' min khalqiin, kama asbt hula' aladhin 'asabathum min qawmika, warahmati wasieat khalqi kllahm, fasa'aktubuha liladhin yakhafun allaha, wayakhshawn eiqabaha, fayudun farayidahu, wayajtanibun maeasiha, waladhin hum bidalayil altawhid wabirahinah yasduquna"